{"tid":2122673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"央視直播成都領事館 傳聞限星期一上午10點撤走","createTime":"2020-07-24T06:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T07:15:26.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ace3babab36589eb02d8088a8f84e1fa7404bd6f","tid":2122673,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:35:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/I9E09BekUH4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FI9E09BekUH4&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6CPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=57d76f7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/I9E09BekUH4</a><br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯內地官媒分析指，「外交尊嚴對等」是中國關閉美國駐成都總領館首要原則，「若美繼續挑釁中方應削減美駐港外交官」，央視亦罕有直播駐成都總領館實況，由約下午1時至下午2時有200萬人次觀看，有網民喊話:「一個都不可以出來」，亦有網民說:「以牙還牙」。<br />\n<br />\n據《環球時報》主編胡錫進消息稱，關於中國要求美方關閉駐成都總領館，按照對等原則，中方也給了美方72小時實施關閉。中方是今天上午10時通知美方這一決定的，這意味著，北京時間星期一上午10點，美駐成都領館需要完成關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200724/NGUBSPUCIZZE6FH2TL76UISQ4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200724%2FNGUBSPUCIZZE6FH2TL76UISQ4U%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6CPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=4adcaaef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200724%2FNGUBSPUCIZZE6FH2TL76UISQ4U%2F&h=b0b93355\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200724/NGUBSPUCIZZE6FH2TL76UISQ4U/</a>"},{"pid":"4ee3ee5965764c64e71fa305b5a96cf2bdc1a4ac","tid":2122673,"uid":153151,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Xz0C0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Xz0C0n.jpg&h=7b7d0741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djateT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djateT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"afb1f49d602519ffe2daeefc553c13426784a049","tid":2122673,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"repl